00:31:08,899 --> 00:31:11,881
♪Your icy tone♪

468
00:31:12,291 --> 00:31:15,416
♪Wounds across lifetimes♪

469
00:31:16,035 --> 00:31:18,605
♪The bitterest tear stains♪

470
00:31:18,605 --> 00:31:22,403
♪Scorch my lips♪

471
00:31:23,075 --> 00:31:25,881
♪Memories pile up, tender and warm♪

472
00:31:26,563 --> 00:31:29,414
♪Our fated bond clings unyielding♪

